name: MultiJS
body:
### MultiJS
MultiJS is a easy2use JavaScript 2.0 Framework for multiple actions.
It includes many functions for ajax, css, effects and more

to build MultiJS from Git (from scratch) do:

```
$ cd path/to/MultiJS/
$ proc gen ./
```

and your done!
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
